citation.case_name: Nelson v. Dretke, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division

html:
542 U.S. 934

NELSON
v.
DRETKE, DIRECTOR, TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF CRIMINAL JUSTICE, CORRECTIONAL INSTITUTIONS DIVISION.

No. 03-8659.

Supreme Court of United States.

June 28, 2004.

1

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari granted, judgment vacated, and case remanded for further consideration in light of Tennard v. Dretke, ante, p. 274. Reported below: 77 Fed. Appx. 209.
